lead_paragraph: France's Kristina Mladenovic will open play against world No. 6 Karolina Pliskova in the Fed Cup final, as the hosts look to break the Czech Republic's stranglehold on the event this weekend.

headline.print_headline: France Bids to Upset Two-Time Champ Czechs in Fed Cup Final
